{
  "stem": "4570.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because as-- as soon as the-- the Germans got it organized, they had those rulings that the Jews have to give their fur coats, their jewelery, and their-- their Persian carpets.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because that was all we really-- never fur coats-- but the other things my mother had-- the only thing was to save, to live from, was for my parents to-- sort of-- just on the outside, to have a divorce.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was just to have an official divorce, not a real divorce.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Which meant that my father lived in a next street where he had to sleep, because there was a curfew at 8 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he came, during-- in the morning, he came back into-- into our place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and in the evening, at 8:00, he had to go again back to-- to where he, you know, where he was officially living.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that-- that-- the only thing that changed at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody knew that because he is divorced from his Aryan wife, that it will cost his life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know that today.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We can all look back and say, why did we do this?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why did we do that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So if he would have stayed in the marriage, he would have been protected right through the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He wouldn't have been sent away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So did your life changed dramatically after that?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, our life changed dramatically only because I had a Jewish boyfriend, and I got very much involved into-- into everything Jewish.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And whatever hurt him, hurt me, or what hurt my father reflected on me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was, you know, I-- perfectly all right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never had to wear a star.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I wasn't threatened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I would not have been deported.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
